=======================================================
== Examples of command line to run tests on 2 nodes. ==
=======================================================

- Standard (without auxiliary script):
--------------------------------------

Node1:

test_dsm_mnD 
    -appName TestDsmMntGcsNode1Unix 
    -gcsDaemonName 8991 
    -batch script_test1_node1.in


Node2:

test_dsm_mnD
    -appName TestDsmMntGcsNode2Unix
    -gcsDaemonName 8991
    -batch script_test1_node2.in


- Non-standard (with auxiliary script):
---------------------------------------

Node1:

test_dsm_mnD 
    -appName TestDsmMntGcsNode1Unix 
    -gcsDaemonName 8991 
    -batch script_test3_node1.in


Node2:

test_dsm_mnD
    -appName MntOnly
    -gcsDaemonName 8991
    -batch script_test3_node2.in


